lead_paragraph: Chris Carter went 3 for 5 with two homers and three RBIs to lead Milwaukee's season-high 18-hit barrage, and the Brewers beat Miami 14-5 on Sunday to snap the Marlins' seven-game winning streak.

headline.print_headline: Brewers Beat Miami 14-5 to Snap Marlins' 7-Game Win Streak
